data.description: Charming, very well kept 3 Bed, 1 Full bath ranch located in a quiet cul-de-sac in the North end of Newark. Home sits on over a half-acre of land with beautiful mature trees. Interior features hardwood and LVP flooring throughout. Home has partially finished basement (accessible from garage). This home sits in a quiet secluded neighborhood with all the feels of country but located very close to The Trout Club and all kinds of other  shopping and dining.
